price: (33) He said, "My Lord, indeed I killed from among them someone, and I fear they will kill me.
arabic: قَالَ رَبِّ إِنِّي قَتَلۡتُ مِنۡهُمۡ نَفۡسٗا فَأَخَافُ أَن يَقۡتُلُونِ
